{"tid":188450,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"呢排聽返周杰倫以前D演唱會","createTime":"2017-04-05T16:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T23:43:35.000Z","uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"904ab7b6f77c77b9044a24332032f892f85da5a3","tid":188450,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"15 J FANS HERE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早前YOUTUBE有條片係話佢演唱會成日忘詞,但又點樣即興得黎仲好聽過原版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便我就聽返佢演唱會版本既歌,都係數返2004年無與倫比最好聽<br />\n唱到同原版唔同之外仲要好聽過CD版,果陣出左碟版真係會係咁LOOP呢個CONCERT,但之後07年個WORLD TOUR已經差好遠,但都有幾首唱得好好聽,07年WORLD TOUR首白色風車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10年超時代就睇氣氛多,首開不了口,同青花瓷X淘汰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但魔天倫隻碟真係好麻麻,D選歌真係唔係好岩聽,但可能始終之前CONCERT都唱太經典,想唱返冷門野<br />\n去到最近地表最強,當聽到佢又黎開,都冇咩意欲去睇,因為都知道會冇咩大驚喜,感覺上都係為奶粉錢而開咁,04年果個充滿既佢真係唔知會唔會再返黎,歲月無情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:佢而家D歌都仲好好聽,只不過希望佢之後演唱會唔好再為開而開,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6fb09d3c7b2b7fdd6355571a03bfc4bd97889b","tid":188450,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:51:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tOwNb9cXgdw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtOwNb9cXgdw&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=6c07f26c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tOwNb9cXgdw</a><br />\n地表最強....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHOLD撚晒比內部既後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 氣氛差到,成班墓地木頭人,本身首歌安排得好好,比真歌迷玩氣氛應該好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" c